so you should issue
the commands.

00:00:21.009 --> 00:00:22.177
Got it.

00:00:22.244 --> 00:00:25.217
Hey, Leo.
You secure our retreat.

00:00:25.284 --> 00:00:27.021
[Tatsuya] Erika, you assist Leo.

00:00:27.087 --> 00:00:28.624
Deal with anyone who tries
to escape.

00:00:28.691 --> 00:00:29.626
[scoffs]

00:00:29.693 --> 00:00:31.195
Don't you want any
of them captured?

00:00:31.262 --> 00:00:33.534
Our top priority
is to neutralize them all.

00:00:33.601 --> 00:00:35.772
Just make sure that gets done,
and safely.

00:00:35.838 --> 00:00:38.711
Chairman, please head
for the rear exit with Kirihara.

00:00:39.278 --> 00:00:42.284
[Tatsuya] Miyuki and I will go
break in head‐on.

00:00:42.351 --> 00:00:44.488
Okay, got it.
That's a good plan.

00:00:46.459 --> 00:00:47.662
<i>[Katsuto] There it is.</i>

00:00:47.729 --> 00:00:50.467
[tires squealing]

00:00:50.535 --> 00:00:51.637
Leo, let's go!

00:00:51.704 --> 00:00:53.373
Enter!

